title: Watch as TOWIE's Bobby Norris is the latest celebrity to be terrified on Tricked - TV
text: Not many things are funnier than watching a celebrity being Tricked, and Ben Hanlin does a great job with TOWIE's Bobby Norris.Believing he is filming a segment on Brighton for This Morning, Bobby has to lob a giant beachball to a guy dressed in a seagull outfit on the pier.What he doesn't know is that it is magician and serial prankster Hanlin inside the outfit.On his second attempt at throwing the beachball, the TOWIE star throws too hard and the seagull loses his balance, falling backwards over the pier and down into the sea below. Bobby is of course horrified and speechless - and it's very funny.Tricked airs tonight (October 13) at 9pm on ITV2.
